{"tid":2155894,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚港台高質節目：《換面》，真係成塊面換撚左!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T16:03:34.000Z","uid":224375,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd028112862487def7d679a323eb7588b305ce8","tid":2155894,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.HK/videos/vb.146094608749288/1130319367399449/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHK.HK%2Fvideos%2Fvb.146094608749288%2F1130319367399449%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=48d82f22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.HK/videos/vb.146094608749288/1130319367399449/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n《零距離科學》 - 換面<br />\n<br />\n面部移植(Face transplantation)，為受槍傷、意外等毀容嘅病人帶來重生嘅希望。今集《零距離科學》同大家講下加拿大第一位經歷面部移植病人嘅故事。<br />\n<br />\n莫里斯．廸士查甸斯2011年被獵槍射傷，失去上下顎、嘴唇、鼻。雖然接受過多次整容手術，都未能恢復樣貌，每日都生活喺痛苦之中。<br />\n<br />\n面部移植嘅機會為莫里斯帶來一絲曙光，不過手術非常複雜，死亡風險好高，仲牽涉倫理道德問題。手術會唔會成功，又值唔值得呢？<br />\n<br />\n《零距離科學》今晚9:30pm #港台電視31/ 31A"},{"pid":"404a7130911c7e723612e7e30ada5dca7f7e318f","tid":2155894,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"Face off"},{"pid":"35089e8b9d8588665beb779bbdac768eedb896bb","tid":2155894,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"之後再去轉韓國執執佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c425e76becf15e83c52900bc8fcf98cb47a69b3a","tid":2155894,"uid":103230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"如眼睛可分對或錯"},{"pid":"33f51625a3f7bfbb4fef745f986401add13d1862","tid":2155894,"uid":97855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c425e76becf15e83c52900bc8fcf98cb47a69b3a","tid":2155894,"uid":103230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score